{"tid":2124413,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"平交道前驚見比基尼豪乳妹！　美女遭虧「赤膊晴子」網暴動","createTime":"2020-07-25T11:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T13:15:22.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c5ef0d75187a25dedb436a35980c4f8468a9a21e","tid":2124413,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T11:05:22.000Z","msg":"PTT表特版近日有網友以「平交道前的比基尼妹」為標題，分享多張截圖照，只見一名比基尼美女，出現在宜蘭礁溪德陽路段平交道前，不僅擁有「神級顏值」還有火爆豪乳，他表示「今天載兒子下課，在平交道前有辣妹在拍照 請問有人知道這是誰嗎？」該則PO文在昨（21號）晚間一出瞬間暴動，該文被網友推到爆，不少人問「這是誰啊？」還有網友以漫畫「灌籃高手」中的經典平交道場景，笑虧美女說是「赤膊晴子」。<br />\n<br />\n原來在PO文中有不少粉絲認出，平交道辣妹應該是近期來台，來自新加坡的亞洲百大DJ Amber藍星蕾，她光是IG就超過百萬粉絲，除了姣好身材吸引不少粉絲，近期更常出現在各大綜藝節目，她在社群平台IG也放上側拍照，被網友認出她脖子上，正是繞著同繽紛色系的比基尼。<br />\n<br />\n稍早藍星蕾臉書也表示：「我都沒發現有網友用行車記錄器在拍我欸，我很認真在拍寫真啦，大家開車要小心❤️注意安全喔！」不少網友留言喊說「哇這好正」、「原圖比修片後的好看太多了」、「超讚圈粉」、「身材臉蛋超棒」還有網友「腦補」開玩笑說「為了拍妹把兒子正在玩的手機硬搶過來」、「兒子：爸爸到底要等幾個紅燈？」、「孩子的媽表示不悅」笑翻一票網友。"},{"pid":"d6c6b13dfdae10b877b381f467e2fcd8abb3326c","tid":2124413,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/04/22/2517241-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F04%2F22%2F2517241-XXL.jpg&h=4a5822bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲網友在PTT表特版貼文發現「平交道比基尼妹」。（圖／翻攝自PTT表特版）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/04/22/2517244-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F04%2F22%2F2517244-XXL.jpg&h=d2fb55ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/04/22/2517231-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F04%2F22%2F2517231-XXL.jpg&h=372b24e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲網友笑虧平交道美女是「赤膊晴子」。（圖／翻攝自PTT表特版）"},{"pid":"2097b5b5dcc3c31c0bf480fac8cc601c6b3d1021","tid":2124413,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T11:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/04/22/2517258-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F04%2F22%2F2517258-XXL.jpg&h=0a67c1a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼有網友憑帶子認出，原來平交道辣妹是DJ藍星蕾。（圖／翻攝自PTT表特版）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/04/22/2517256-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F04%2F22%2F2517256-XXL.jpg&h=e35612b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7fea62c9100750ce23f663f8120294e828fcc2b","tid":2124413,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T11:08:17.000Z","msg":"仲入到台"},{"pid":"8eeb71bdd01e72f8b46340b248615b4d24bf070c","tid":2124413,"uid":326725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T11:11:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原圖比修片後的好看太多了</blockquote><br />\n修圖反而唔夠原圖好睇？<br />\n咁修圖嘅意義喺邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e0fbcbd5cb8c0ef1e00aa63271b659c6fac278","tid":2124413,"uid":127955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T11:20:28.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"f6edcd7612e796e17b60411202c70e6f57176130","tid":2124413,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T13:13:59.000Z","msg":"佢居然入到台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89930c5ed45588bcf1dd07c7f1668f681a633194","tid":2124413,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T13:15:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}